## Limitations
The findings are based on a limited number of studies and may not fully capture the diversity of experiences among middle-aged individuals. Additionally, cultural and socioeconomic factors that influence decision-making were not extensively covered in the available sources. Further research is needed to explore these dimensions comprehensively.

